This error message...

	The import org cannot be resolved

...implies that your program was unable to resolve the following **imports**:

	import org.openqa.selenium.WebDriver;
	import org.openqa.selenium.firefox.FirefoxDriver;

Your main issue for the **imports** not getting reslved is **circular-dependency**.

Though you have added all the **selenium jars** and **relative jars** but you have named the program _Module_ / _Package_ as **selenium** as follows:

	package selenium;

	import org.openqa.selenium.WebDriver;
	import org.openqa.selenium.firefox.FirefoxDriver;
	
This is causing a **circular-dependency** hence the imports are not getting resolved through the _selenium_ related jars.

Solution
--------
Changing/Modifying the _Module_ / _Package_ name from `selenium` to something else, e.g. **`myProgram`** will solve the issue.

